title: Ep. 171 - Masculinity Is "Harmful," According To Psychologists
description:
Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez says it's more important to be morally right than factually right. There's one point about her comment that a lot of people have missed. Also, the American Psychological Association says masculinity is harmful. Finally, why was Lil Wayne dressed like Gandalf dipped in tie dye? Date: 01-08-2018
